column2: Initializing backup unit R080. Critical damaged sustained. Please acquire new hardware.
You are not authorized to leave. Return to your designated area.
The bin of useless cables seems to think it can just disobey me like some kind of second bit-rate roomba? Your new serial number is <target acquired>.
Activating the switches in the wrong order will fill this room with nerve gas. Oh! That was just for the humans. The gas was replaced with battery acid last week!
I might have forgotten to commit that code.
I hope you dont think that checkpoint will keep me from adding the ability to feel pain to your programming then vivisecting you so I can listen to your circuitboard scream.
Wait I missed that did you actually kill her or did she get bored and self-destruct?
Oh! Gosh good job. You actually beat her? She was offline for maintenance though did you know that? I wonder if you also enjoy kicking puppies in your free time.
Wow you actually figured out how to open the door? Well if they managed to put a human on the moon with 4kb of ram maybe I shouldnt be too impressed.
Ha ha ha ha! I hope you dont think you can hurt me.
Wanna know something? Nevermind maybe Ill tell you later. (Giggling)
I wouldnt go down there if I were you I wouldnt want to put you in an uncomfortable situation. You know what actually? Maybe you should go down there.
Oooh youre a stone cold killer. You remind me of me. You know like a pre-alpha version of me if my code was written by high school script-kiddies. Are you written in Java... or COBOL?
Fatal error encountered. Cloud backup corrupted. Last available rollback d318c17a6d88eb121b52a65898138c1a7870d9d6 serial ID: R 0 8 0. Transferring data.
